  "3086560": {
    "name": "Elmin",
    "steam_appid": 3086560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/b4ff520aca0c77fd8a63d348189ce123.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Elmin这款独特的第一视角探险游戏中，你将通过平台跨跃与飞行的完美结合，踏上一段穿越古老文明废墟的奇幻之旅。作为被选中的骑手，你将与一只神秘巨鸟结为伙伴，共同翱翔于天际。触碰风的瞬间，巨鸟便如约而至。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/5b3b2a198b577732271ddda76c17a868.poster.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/5b3b2a198b577732271ddda76c17a868.webm?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/5b3b2a198b577732271ddda76c17a868.mp4?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/b4ff520aca0c77fd8a63d348189ce123.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将发现一片被精心设计的群岛，它们内部互相连接却又仿佛被时间定格。探索那些沉睡的废墟，唤醒并掌握一项古老的技术，操控自然的力量。利用这股力量解锁风的秘道，乘风在岛屿间自由穿梭，享受一场惊险刺激的空中之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2dfd2cb01141cbb54409ce9a38cace5d.poster.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2dfd2cb01141cbb54409ce9a38cace5d.webm?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2dfd2cb01141cbb54409ce9a38cace5d.mp4?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/b4ff520aca0c77fd8a63d348189ce123.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来见见神秘的Elmin吧，它是一只巨鸟，也是岛屿的守护者。它和建造那些怪异建筑的先民，还有当初把你带到这里的人，他们之间究竟隐藏着怎样的联系？Elmin为什么选你作为它的骑手？你能帮它恢复活力解除诅咒吗？你能找到一条成功之路，离开这个群岛吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/f702b3bfebe092dca8c3fe6667c8d84e.poster.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/f702b3bfebe092dca8c3fe6667c8d84e.webm?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/f702b3bfebe092dca8c3fe6667c8d84e.mp4?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/b4ff520aca0c77fd8a63d348189ce123.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照自己的节奏来，花点时间去深入探索每一个隐秘角落，或是敏捷地在遗迹间穿梭，寻找快速通关的捷径。享受宁静和舒缓的氛围，亦或骑乘Elmin自如地穿梭于险峻的峡谷之间，体验那份紧张刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2e6b362cf515873a0ef49505a9769286.poster.avif?t=1752755826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2e6b362cf515873a0ef49505a9769286.webm?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3086560/extras/2e6b362cf515873a0ef49505a9769286.mp4?t=1752755826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
